select
    id,
    display_name,
    creation_date,
    last_access_date,
    profile_image_url,
    (
        select count(*) from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`question_stats`
        where owner_user_id = filtered_users.id
    ) as questions_posted,
    (
        select sum(upvote_count) from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`question_stats`
        where owner_user_id = filtered_users.id
    ) as questions_posted_upvotes,
    (
        select sum(downvote_count) from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`question_stats`
        where owner_user_id = filtered_users.id
    ) as questions_posted_downvotes,
    (
        select sum(answer_count) from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`question_stats`
        where owner_user_id = filtered_users.id
    ) as answers_inspired,
    (
        select count(*) from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`answer_stats`
        where owner_user_id = filtered_users.id
    ) as answers_posted,
    (
        select sum(upvote_count) from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`answer_stats`
        where owner_user_id = filtered_users.id
    ) as answers_posted_upvotes,
    (
        select sum(downvote_count) from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`answer_stats`
        where owner_user_id = filtered_users.id
    ) as answers_posted_downvotes
from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`filtered_users`

with questions as (
    select
        DATE_TRUNC(DATE(creation_date), DAY) AS `day`,
        count(*) as num_questions
    from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`filtered_questions`
    group by `day`
),
answers as (
    select
        DATE_TRUNC(DATE(creation_date), DAY) AS `day`,
        count(*) as num_answers
    from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`filtered_answers`
    group by `day`
),
askers as (
    select
        DATE_TRUNC(DATE(creation_date), DAY) AS `day`,
        count(distinct(owner_user_id)) as num_askers
    from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`filtered_questions`
    group by `day`
),
answerers as (
    select
        DATE_TRUNC(DATE(creation_date), DAY) AS `day`,
        count(distinct(owner_user_id)) as num_answerers
    from `community-gcp-sandbox`.`stackostudy`.`filtered_answers`
    group by `day`
)

select
    questions.day as `day`,
    questions.num_questions,
    answers.num_answers,
    askers.num_askers,
    answerers.num_answerers
from questions
left join answers on answers.day = questions.day
left join askers on askers.day = questions.day
left join answerers on answerers.day = questions.day
order by `day` desc
